Package: epicdata
Title: Clean Data for Epidemiology
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Felix", "Forster", , "forsterepi@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre","cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3670-9244"))
Description: A workflow for processing of epidemiological data, turning your 
    raw data into data that can be analyzed. You provide raw data and specify
    metadata in YAML using a user-friendly format. Decisions regarding invalid
    values can be collected in spreadsheet files. `epicdata` is thus suitable
    for non-veteran R users.
License: GPL (>= 3)
